-----

-   See Also: [WordPress
    Taxonomy](/WordPress_Taxonomy "WordPress Taxonomy").
-   Uses:
    [`taxonomy_exists()`](/Function_Reference/taxonomy_exists "Function Reference/taxonomy exists")
    Checks whether taxonomy exists.
-   Uses:
    [`get_taxonomy()`](/Function_Reference/get_taxonomy "Function Reference/get taxonomy")
    Used to get the taxonomy object.

Change Log
----------

Since: 2.3.0

Source File
-----------

`is_taxonomy_hierarchical()` is located in `wp-includes/taxonomy.php`.

